Level 10

	Playfair cipher is a manual symmetric encryption technique and first 
	digram substitution cipher.Here, a "Keyword" and 5*5 matrix are used 
	to encrypt the plaintext.
	
        Cipher text for the password of the next level given by
	"ADTIKAAKCZAOFQGYVBRLQFFGCPTIDWKA"

	HINT: Given a plaintext-ciphertext pair,

	Plaintext : 
		P.C. MAHALANOBIS WAS AFFILIATED WITH SEVERAL ORGANIZATIONS. HE FOUNDED THE INDIAN 
		STATISTICAL INSTITUTE IN CALCUTTA. IN THE NEXT TWO DECADES HE FOUNDED THE NATIONAL 
		SAMPLE SURVEY AND THE CENTRAL STATISTICAL ORGANIZATION TO SERVE AS STATISTICAL 
		AGENCIES FOR GOVERNMENT DATA COLLECTION.
	Ciphertext:
		UOAHLHNHMCISIXLBHERFHSLQFEXBRLBGWEQHMSTFHMCXLQSBLC. 
		AFDIZCEFGPAFCHFOHMGYLQSCRSBNHSLCRSUPQGCHBNNSPUQL. 
		CHRLKAFWRYYRVBEFBNEFILFGCPMKFERLKALQSBMHSGHATMGBPTWDWLMKRLKBKAUTHNGY
                LQSCRSBNMSTFHMCXLQSBLUBCFQWDLBGYLQSCRSBNHNKFCKBFIGIPDSDWUHADLOEMQLOBHYYHKBRSCM.

